data.description: Motivated Sellers!! Come see this beautifully remodeled home in the well established, quiet Edgmere subdivision. The interior features new paint, flooring, light fixtures, granite countertops, cabinets, and appliances! New large vinyl windows make this home wonderful and bright!! Brand new roof was installed in April 2023. There is a large split room that gives the flexibility of a large den, media room, or home office! This home is move-in ready!
